    "This innovative cycle culminates in the Residual HSRCNN framework, marking a significant advancement in hyperspectral image reconstruction.",
    "The loss function of HSRCNN is outlined in Eq. 13.",
    "where, Z = Output hyperspectral image, Z = Estimated hyperspectral output from the model, Y =Input RGB Image.",
